overview: Want to be a track rat for a day? Go behind the scenes at a horse race track and discover what it takes to make an equestrian winner. You know the question on everyone's mind as they enter the stands: 'Who do you like?' Find out how to spot the winners and what it takes to be on a winning team as you follow a jockey around on a typical day leading up to the day: Race Day!
title: Who Do You Like?
